int main(){
	ios::sync_with_stdio(0);
	int t;
	cin >> t;
	while(t--){
		long long n, l;
		cin >> n >> l;
		vector<pair<long long, int> > a;
		vector<long long> ans, finalAns;
		a.resize(n);
		ans.resize(n);
		for(int i = 0; i < n; i++){
			cin >> a[i].first;
			a[i].second = i;
		}
		sort(a.begin(), a.end());
		if(a[0].first != 1 || a[n-1].first >= l){
			printf("-1\n");
			continue;
		}
		bool declared = false;
		for(int i = 0; i < n-1; i++){
			if(a[i+1].first % a[i].first){
				declared = true;
				printf("-1\n");
				break;
			}
			ans[a[i].second] = (a[i+1].first/a[i].first) - 1;
		}
		if(declared) continue;
		ans[a[n-1].second] = (l - a[n-1].first + 1)/a[n-1].first;
		long long val = 0;
		for(int i = 0; i < n; i++){
			val += ans[a[i].second] * a[i].first;
			// trace2(ans[a[i].second], a[i].first);
		}

		if(val != l){
			printf("-1\n");
			continue;
		}
		for(int i = 0; i < n; i++){
			printf("%lld ", ans[i]);
		}
		printf("\n");
	}
}
